### Thanks for taking the time to contribute! :tada:

## How Can I Contribute?

**Developers**:
> - Making new functions.
> - Founding bugs on actual code.
> - Coding Improvements.

**Translators**:
> - All languages for the time being.

**Media cretors**:
> - Media for Twitter.
> - Logo, emblem, figure, symbol.
> - Youtube Videos.
